<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.10">
<l>cīrārneṭu maṟukiṉciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>tērārmukil vaṇṇaṉṟaṉai yimaiyōrperu māṉai</l>
<l>kārārvayal maṅkaikkiṟai kaliyaṉoli mālai</l>
<l>pārārivai paravittoḻap pāvampayi lāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If those of earth worship, singing this garland of verse</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ, chief of Maṅkai with rain-filled fields,</l>
<l>About the great lord of the unblinking [celestials],</l>
<l rend="indent">the one of beautiful cloud hue</l>
<l>On the watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr with fine, long streets,</l>
<l rend="indent">evil will not befall [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
